review_text:
A little bit of a different kind of a movie, _Siberia_ does not seem quite sure what sort of viewing experience it wants to be, but it's okay. The leads are quite good and it managed to keep me more or less engaged from start to finish (and especially for that finish).

_Final rating:★★½ - Had a lot that appealed to me, didn’t quite work as a whole._
